  <brief_title>A Study of Mapatumumab in Combination With Sorafenib in Subjects With Advanced Hepatocellular Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <acronym>HCC</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 1B, Multi-center, Open Label, Dose Escalation Study of Mapatumumab ([HGS1012], a Fully-human Monoclonal Antibody to TRAIL-R1) in Combination With Sorafenib as a First Line Therapy in Subjects With Advanced Hepatocellular Carcinoma</official_title>
