  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and tolerability of escalating doses of
      mapatumumab in combination with sorafenib in subjects with advanced Hepatocellular Carcinoma
      who are positive for hepatitis B surface antigen or hepatitis C antibody.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
